<div class="content" name="MapDBChar" uuid="a527d694-bd9e-4d9d-affc-e1b172612d2d"><p>Loop through the table, returning a substitution character
if a match is found. If no match is found, return the original character.</p><dl>
<dd>
<div><pre> FOR each Row in SubstitutionTable
     IF Row (0) is TempChar THEN
         RETURN Row (1)
     END IF
 END FOR
 RETURN TempChar
  
</pre></div>
</dd></dl></div>